1617static int
1618nvkm_device_pci_preinit(struct nvkm_device *device)
1619{
1620 struct nvkm_device_pci *pdev = nvkm_device_pci(device);
1621 if (pdev->suspend) {
1622#ifndef __NetBSD__ /* XXX pmf takes care of this for us. */
1623 int ret = pci_enable_device(pdev->pdev);
1624 if (ret)
1625 return ret;
1626 pci_set_master(pdev->pdev);
1627#endif
1628 pdev->suspend = false;
1629 }
1630 return 0;
1631}

1665
1666int
1667nvkm_device_pci_new(struct pci_dev *pci_dev, const char *cfg, const char *dbg,
1668 bool detect, bool mmio, u64 subdev_mask,
1669 struct nvkm_device **pdevice)
1670{
1671 const struct nvkm_device_quirk *quirk = NULL;
1672 const struct nvkm_device_pci_device *pcid;
1673 const struct nvkm_device_pci_vendor *pciv;
1674 const char *name = NULL;
1675 struct nvkm_device_pci *pdev;
1676#ifndef __NetBSD__
1677 int ret;
1678#endif
1679
1680#ifndef __NetBSD__
1681 ret = pci_enable_device(pci_dev);
1682 if (ret)
1683 return ret;
1684#endif
1685
1686 switch (pci_dev->vendor) {
1687 case 0x10de: pcid = nvkm_device_pci_10de; break;
1688 default:
1689 pcid = NULL;
1690 break;
1691 }
1692
1693 while (pcid && pcid->device) {
1694 if (pciv = pcid->vendor, pcid->device == pci_dev->device) {
1695 while (pciv && pciv->vendor) {
1696 if (pciv->vendor == pci_dev->subsystem_vendor &&
1697 pciv->device == pci_dev->subsystem_device) {
1698 quirk = &pciv->quirk;
1699 name = pciv->name;
1700 break;
1701 }
1702 pciv++;
1703 }
1704 if (!name)
1705 name = pcid->name;
1706 break;
1707 }
1708 pcid++;
1709 }
1710
1711 if (!(pdev = kzalloc(sizeof(*pdev), GFP_KERNEL))) {
1712 linux_pci_disable_device(pci_dev);
1713 return -ENOMEM;
1714 }
1715 *pdevice = &pdev->device;
1716 pdev->pdev = pci_dev;
1717
1718 return nvkm_device_ctor(&nvkm_device_pci_func, quirk,
1719 pci_dev_dev(pci_dev),
1720 pci_is_pcie(pci_dev) ? NVKM_DEVICE_PCIE :
1721 pci_find_capability(pci_dev, PCI_CAP_ID_AGP) ?
1722 NVKM_DEVICE_AGP : NVKM_DEVICE_PCI,
1723 (u64)pci_domain_nr(pci_dev->bus) << 32 |
1724 pci_dev->bus->number << 16 |
1725 PCI_SLOT(pci_dev->devfn) << 8 |
1726 PCI_FUNC(pci_dev->devfn), name,
1727 cfg, dbg, detect, mmio, subdev_mask,
1728 &pdev->device);
1729}
